
---

## 📊 Folder Overview

| Folder | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `/assets` | Logo, screenshots, demo video |
| `/data` | Example datasets for freelancers & gigs |
| `/automation` | Make.com & Zapier automations |
| `/docs` | Setup, Glide structure, API connection |
| `/` | README + License |

